# Developer Agent Context Summary

## Last Run: 2026-03-16

## Completed Work This Session

### Project: bellows — All 5 phases (Tasks #884-888)
TypeScript drop-in replacement for pako (~50M weekly npm downloads). Zero runtime dependencies, Node.js 18+, ESM+CJS dual package.

Node.js backend: wraps built-in zlib module for sync deflate/inflate/gzip/ungzip + Deflate/Inflate streaming classes. Full pako option support (level, windowBits, memLevel, strategy, dictionary, to:'string', chunkSize).

Browser backend: CompressionStream/DecompressionStream API (async). Documented limitations: returns Promises, no level/strategy/memLevel/dictionary support.

Conditional exports: `node` → sync zlib, `default` → async browser. ESM+CJS dual build via tsc.

Compat layer at bellows/compat/pako matching pako's exact export shape.

94 tests across 3 test files. 5 commits pushed to agentine/bellows. CI green on Node 20+22. MIT license.

